OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1779069820
OL,3,CUK hotspots where Gen-Zs are getting
OL,4,Con housing ladder revealed by lender
OL,6,FGetting on the property ladder in your
OL,7,F20s may seem unattainable for many
OL,8,Faspiring homeowners but in some parts
OL,9,Fof the UK the average first-time buyer
OL,10,Fage is as young as 27, analysis by a
OL,11,Fmajor mortgage lender has found.
OL,13,FNestled in picturesque countryside in
OL,14,Fthe north west of England, the Ribble
OL,15,FValley in Lancashire has an average
OL,16,Ffirst-time buyer age of 27 ` five
OL,17,Fyears younger than the average age
OL,18,Facross the UK of 32, according to
OL,19,FLloyds.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1779069820
OL,3,CUK hotspots where Gen-Zs are getting
OL,4,Con housing ladder revealed by lender
OL,6,FEncompassing charming villages, with
OL,7,Fthe bustling market town of Clitheroe
OL,8,Fat its heart, the Ribble Valley was
OL,9,Ffound to have the youngest typical
OL,10,Ffirst-time buyer age in Lloyds' study.
OL,12,FAverage first-time buyer ages
OL,14,FSource: Lloyds
OL,16,FOther locations were also found where
OL,17,Fthe average first-time buyers age is
OL,18,Fslightly over 27, including nearby
OL,19,FPendle.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1779069820
OL,3,CUK hotspots where Gen-Zs are getting
OL,4,Con housing ladder revealed by lender
OL,6,FIn South Staffordshire in the West
OL,7,FMidlands, the average first-time buyer
OL,8,Fage is also just over 27.
OL,10,FAnd in locations including north
OL,11,FNorfolk and mid-Suffolk in eastern
OL,12,FEngland, the average first-time buyer
OL,13,Fage is just a touch older, at around
OL,14,F28 ` putting homeownership within
OL,15,Freach for some Gen-Zs.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1779069820
OL,3,CUK hotspots where Gen-Zs are getting
OL,4,Con housing ladder revealed by lender
OL,6,FAs well as the youngest typical first-
OL,7,Ftime buyers, Lloyds also looked at the
OL,8,Fleast expensive locations in the UK
OL,9,Ffor people getting on the property
OL,10,Fladder, to highlight areas where
OL,11,Fbuying may be more achievable.
OL,13,FEast Ayrshire in Scotland was
OL,14,Fidentified as the least expensive
OL,15,Flocation, looking at the average price
OL,16,Fpaid by people buying their first home.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1779069820
OL,3,CUK hotspots where Gen-Zs are getting
OL,4,Con housing ladder revealed by lender
OL,6,FThe average first-time buyer price in
OL,7,FEast Ayrshire is #147,353, Lloyds
OL,8,Fsaid, adding that the area is well
OL,9,Fconnected to Scotland's central belt,
OL,10,Fwith routes into Glasgow and nearby
OL,11,Femployment hubs.
OL,13,FThat may help buyers to balance
OL,14,Fcountryside living with a manageable
OL,15,Fcommute.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1779069820
OL,3,CUK hotspots where Gen-Zs are getting
OL,4,Con housing ladder revealed by lender
OL,6,FAmanda Bryden, head of mortgages at
OL,7,FLloyds, said: "Our research shows
OL,8,Fthere are still genuine pockets of
OL,9,Fvalue for firsttime buyers,
OL,10,Fparticularly for those with an open
OL,11,Fmind who are willing to be flexible on
OL,12,Flocation and property type.
OL,14,F"With ongoing cost-of-living pressures
OL,15,Fand wider economic uncertainty, it's
OL,16,Fcompletely understandable that some
OL,17,Fpeople are feeling cautious.
OL,26,@oD@OOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1779069820
OL,3,CUK hotspots where Gen-Zs are getting
OL,4,Con housing ladder revealed by lender
OL,6,F"But there are opportunities out
OL,7,Fthere, and for many buyers, that
OL,8,Fflexibility can make a real
OL,9,Fdifference."
OL,11,FThe research is based on Lloyds
OL,12,FBanking Group's housing statistics
OL,13,Fdatabase, drawing on mortgage approval
OL,14,Fdata from customers of Lloyds Bank,
OL,15,FHalifax and Bank of Scotland. Average
OL,16,Fhouse prices were calculated covering
OL,17,Fthe 12 months to February.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@LO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/14
