PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1779069820
OL,3,CUK hotspots where Gen-Zs are getting
OL,4,Con housing ladder revealed by lender
OL,6,FGiving general tips to first-time
OL,7,Fbuyers, Ms Bryden suggested that they
OL,8,Fdo their research on the home-buying
OL,9,Fprocess, speak to a mortgage
OL,10,Fprofessional early on and consider the
OL,11,Fdifferent types of support available.
OL,13,FLast week, Lloyds announced it is
OL,14,Flaunching a new low-deposit mortgage
OL,15,Ftoday that could help first-time
OL,16,Fbuyers get on the property ladder with
OL,17,Fa deposit as low as #5,000.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/14
